In the MATTER OF the Petition to Restore the License of Kenneth ZAHL, M.D. License No. MA56413 to Practice Medicine and Surgery in the State of New Jersey (Kenneth Zahl, M.D. - Movant) M-1023/1024/1025 September Term 2018
081565 Supreme Court of New Jersey. June 8, 2019

ORDER

It is ORDERED that the miscellaneous motion to amend the record to include the documents contained in the Appellate Division appendix on appeal in A-002607-15, but omitted from the copies filed with the Supreme Court (M-1023) is granted; and it is further

ORDERED that the miscellaneous motions for the Court to take original jurisdiction (M-1024), or alternatively, for a remand (M-1025) are denied.
